data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT! Fully fenced, two story home with great curb appeal! Family room w/ lots of natural light and built-in shelving. The sunken living room has a wood burning fireplace. Lost of cabinet and counterspace in the kitchen, nice size formal dining area. Spacious bedrooms with large closets. Large master bedroom with master bathroom is separate from other bedrooms. Basement provides additional storage and laundry room. Nice patio with side gate access, mature trees, garage and a carport. A must see!
